# kb/learned/ — intentionally empty at setup.
#
# This folder is filled AUTOMATICALLY later by the feedback loop (Stages 3–4),
# NOT by hand:
#   - validated agent replies      -> ticket-<id>.md      (similarity >= 0.7)
#   - owner Q&A answers            -> owner-qa-<ts>.md
#
# Kept as a separate folder so the owner can review/prune machine-grown
# knowledge. Files here may carry extra front-matter (ticket_id, source_type,
# review_pending, created_at) per kb/CONVENTIONS.md §2.
#
# This .gitkeep keeps the empty folder in Git until the first learned file lands.
